{
  "page": "Years of Shame",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p>The <b>Years of Shame</b> were a period in the history of the <a href=\"/index.php/Summer_Isles\" title=\"Summer Isles\">Summer Isles</a>, which lasted for two centuries. During this time, native princes sold defeated rivals to <a href=\"/index.php/Slavery\" title=\"Slavery\">slavers</a> from the <a href=\"/index.php/Ghiscari_Empire\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Ghiscari Empire\">Ghiscari Empire</a>, the <a href=\"/index.php/Valyrian_Freehold\" title=\"Valyrian Freehold\">Valyrian Freehold</a>&#160;and the <a href=\"/index.php/Basilisk_Isles\" title=\"Basilisk Isles\">Basilisk Isles</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiafbeyond_the_free_cities:_the_summer_isles.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiafbeyond_the_free_cities:_the_summer_isles.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>The Years of Shame ended when <a href=\"/index.php/Xanda_Qo\" title=\"Xanda Qo\">Xanda Qo</a>, Princess of <a href=\"/index.php/Sweet_Lotus_Vale\" title=\"Sweet Lotus Vale\">Sweet Lotus Vale</a> and a former slave, united the isles under her rule. Under her rule, <a href=\"/index.php/Swan_ship\" title=\"Swan ship\">swan ships</a> were introduced and sailors employed <a href=\"/index.php/Goldenheart\" title=\"Goldenheart\">goldenheart</a> bows to resist encroaching slaver raids.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiafbeyond_the_free_cities:_the_summer_isles.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiafbeyond_the_free_cities:_the_summer_isles.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Years_of_Shame&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rtwoiafbeyond_the_free_cities:_the_summer_isles.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">↑ <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rtwoiafbeyond_the_free_cities:_the_summer_isles.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\">1.0</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rtwoiafbeyond_the_free_cities:_the_summer_isles.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\">1.1</a></sup></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/The_World_of_Ice_%26_Fire\" title=\"The World of Ice &amp; Fire\">The World of Ice &amp; Fire</a></i>, Beyond the Free Cities: The Summer Isles.</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260404215635\nCache expiry: 1209600\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.010 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.011 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 172/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 8568/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 830/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 436/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 7/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\nUnstrip recursion depth: 0/20\nUnstrip post‐expand size: 1098/5000000 bytes\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%    7.129      1 -total\n 75.59%    5.389      2 Template:Ref\n 43.68%    3.114      2 Template:Ref/core\n 22.65%    1.615      1 Template:References\n-->\n</div>\n<!-- Saved in parser cache with key westeros_awoiaftest-mw_:pcache:idhash:38652-0!canonical and timestamp 20260404215635 and revision id 323558\n -->\n",
